functionDescription: This function extends the call info list in a Lua state by adding a new CallInfo node to it.

outputInterfaces.name: ci
outputInterfaces.meaning: New CallInfo node added to the list

outputInterfaces.name: ret
outputInterfaces.meaning: Return value, which is the new CallInfo node

inoutInterfaces.name: L
inoutInterfaces.meaning: The Lua state in which the CallInfo list is extended
